entries.femaleVariant: [Open]
H-he's here! Randy!
He's hangin' in there! We made it! V, shut down the machine. Can't unlink Randy otherwise.
Hurry! Gotta shut it off!
[Turn off]
[Remove]
It's OK, don't-don't be scared. We're here to help. A bit dehydrated, but you are gonna be fine.
entries.maleVariant: It's OK, don't be scared. We're here to help. You're a bit dehydrated, but you're gonna be fine.

entries.femaleVariant: Been dead a few days already...
[Remove]
[Remove]
Alive... Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa, easy there, you're all right now.
entries.maleVariant: Alive... Whoa, whoa, easy there, easy now. Hey, you're all right now.

entries.femaleVariant: No, no, kid, please... Shit, he's not breathing!
Get that fucking computer off!
Poor kid…
Must've died a few days back…
Got a pulse, but it's weak. Need to get him to a hospital, quick.
entries.maleVariant: I got a pulse, but it's weak. We need to get him to a hospital, quick.

entries.femaleVariant: [Teleport to farm]
The horror that bastard inflicted... Can't let it go.
Do whatcha gotta do, but count me out.
Don't do it, River.
I'll help you.
Do whatcha gotta do. Kill him, spare him... Just one request, River...
Not willin' to see this through with me?
Too bad. Thought we'd take this to the end together. But it's all right, I'll handle it.
River, come on, man... It won't change anything.
entries.maleVariant: River, c'mon, man... It won't change anything.

entries.femaleVariant: Anthony Harris is a sad sack of meat hooked up to a respirator now.
entries.maleVariant: Anthony Harris is a sad sack of meat, hooked up to a respirator now.

entries.femaleVariant: Ugh, I dunno. Maybe you're right. But it's drivin' me crazy not doin' anything.
No, River. Want that fucker's blood on my hands, too.
Gonna take him out in my own way, amidst all this confusion.
You alive? C'mon, eyes open. Help's on the way.
entries.maleVariant: You alive? C'mon, c'mon, eyes open. Help's on the way.

entries.femaleVariant: Too late for this one…
Breathin', good. Hey, just hold on a bit longer.
entries.maleVariant: Breathin', good. Just hold on a bit longer.

entries.femaleVariant: Randy? Hey, you got this, buddy. Here with your uncle. It's gonna be all right.
entries.maleVariant: Randy? Hey, you got this, buddy. I'm here with your uncle. It's gonna be all right.

entries.femaleVariant: You alive?
Randy?
Hope it isn't too late...
Hey, kid...
River, this is the farm! We got it!
entries.maleVariant: River, this is the farm! We got it.

entries.femaleVariant: The barn! Quick!
I know. Let's get to the barn, quick.
Leave me out of it. Had my fill of this case.
Appreciate your dedication, V... but this is between me and Harris.
Randy! Don't you do this to me, kid.
Yep, we sure did. But I'm not about leave it like this.
Do whatcha gotta do, but count me out.
Don't do it, River.
We both will.
We fucked up, River...
Yep, we sure did. But it is far from over.
Besides, I shouldn't've asked for your help to begin with. It was a dumb call.
Knew from the start I shoulda hired a professional. Not you.
Grab something!
Hey, are you alive?
Hey, kid…
I'm sorry, buddy…
Shit, too late…?
We fucked up…
[Turn off]
Security systems neutralized!
Nice work!
10-52, I repeat, I've got a 10-52 at a farm south of the city.
Oh, and watch for automated defenses on site. They're substantial.
See that coyote?
Yes, send the fucking squad!
Yeah, relaying coordinates now... No, several, at least... Do it quick, dammit.
Not good...
We did it, River.
What's that?
Helped you 'cause it was about your nephew. That's over, so enough.
For how long? He has to die. It's the only way I'll be sure.
Stop. Gonna throw your life away gettin' revenge on a braindead vegetable?
Like dodgy takeout…
Grenade or anti-personnel mine. Gotta be careful.
What's your plan?
They nabbed him already. He's not goin' anywhere.
Whaddaya wanna do? Zero him?
He's in a coma, in police custody. He's not gettin' away with anything.
Exactly. Squeeze the life out of him with my bare hands.
Sick fuck has to die.
He's still alive. So in a sense, he is gettin' away with it... Not for long, though.
Gonna squeeze the life outta him with my bare hands.
Best of luck.
Really aim to do this?
Best of luck, then.
Really aim to do it? They'll catch you.
No they won't.
I'm... Well… That is, I was a detective, remember? I know how to cover my tracks.
See each other around?
Probably, eventually. Need a little time to myself for now.
Really, V, thanks. Couldn't've done it without you.
Don't mention it. And holo if you need anything.
Forget about Harris and go on with your life.
Forget about Harris. Take one day at a time. But rest first.
Actually, got quite a bit you can do, River.
Joss and Randy'll need you now.
Joss, Randy, the kids... They're gonna need you now more than ever.
entries.maleVariant: Joss, Randy, the kids... They're gonna need you now, more than ever.

entries.femaleVariant: Yeah... No, you're right…
Once your head's on straight again, gimme a holo. We'll talk.
No problem. Don't be a stranger.
entries.maleVariant: No problem. Hey, don't be a stranger.

entries.femaleVariant: Just remember you can count on me.
Just remember – say the word, I'm there. You can count on me.
Sure you don't want help? They'll catch you.
Sure you wanna do this alone?
No they won't. I'm... Well... That is, I was a detective, remember?
I know how to cover my tracks.
Need a little time to myself now… But I'll remember.
Don't mention it. And holler if you change your mind. Or, if you're just in the mood to holler.
Psychoscum's gonna pay for it.
What's your plan?
They nabbed him already. He's not goin' anywhere.
Don't get caught.
You blame me?
Whatever you decide... don't get caught.
Like it matters.
Still, thanks. For tryin' to help.
Yeah, for tryin'...
Hang on, you tryna to blame for me for the fuck-up?
You're grieving, so I'll forget you said that.
Yeah, forget it. Forget everything.
It was my mistake. Thought you could help me, that we'd fare better together.
Joss will need you now.
You blame me?
Just... take it one day at a time. Y'still got Joss.
Her and the kiddos'll need Uncle River more than ever.
entries.maleVariant: Her and the kiddos will need Uncle River more than ever.

entries.femaleVariant: Yeah, got a point... Anyway, thanks for tryin' to help.
Yeah, for tryin'...
So kill him yourself, then.
You blame me?
So please, zero the fucker yourself then. Enjoy kickin' it in prison after.
entries.maleVariant: So please, zero the fucker yourself then. And enjoy kickin' it in prison after.

entries.femaleVariant: Like I care.
But despite all this... thanks for tryin' to help.
Yeah, for tryin'...
Cameras and turrets're linked... It's a goddamn shooting range.
Sure are a lotta cameras here…
Breathe a bit. Got the last stretch to the barn left.
V! Get down!
Careful, River! Watch the mines!
OK, all disconnected!
Check the others! Could still be alive.
Right!
OK, all disconnected!
Check the others! We gotta try to help, even if it means just saving one.
On it.
V! V, he's not responding! H-help him, please!
V! H-help me with Randy!
Dammit! Right behind you!
Yeah, need a little time to myself now. But then I'll call ya. I will.
[Stand]
River! C'mere, quick!
Oh fuck...
[Release]
Heads up! Turrets are live! The system controlling them must be in the house.
By the barn, two more turrets. That front gate's a death trap.
Got cables comin' outta this wall. Should be a switch somewhere.
It's gotta be here! Have a look around.
Try disabling the defense system then haul ass to the barn!
Dammit. Locked up tight. Need to find another way...
V, wrong way! Randy needs us NOW, you forget that?!
There we go...
Poor bastard... You just left him.
Yeah. Yeah, I did.
Hey, we're ready for evac. Are you riding along or not?
Poor boys… All your years, ever seen anything like this?
Area is secure, all witnesses questioned, and victims are en route.
Eight years on the force, nothin' comes close... Beyond twisted.
Have Ramirez debrief with her boys here. They'll be gathering evidence till morning.
[Release]
[Release]
Shut down that damned contraption, V!
Help me!
Need to loosen this, help me!
[Get out]
[Get out]
